messages.content:
Found it. The rich text renderer is pulling in the entire Notion SDK:

```javascript
// Before
import { Client } from '@notionhq/client';

// Problem: full SDK is 340kb minified
// We only use: blocks.getBlockChildren()
```

Replaced with a targeted fetch:
```javascript
// After
const response = await fetch(
  `https://api.notion.com/v1/blocks/${blockId}/children`,
  { headers: { Authorization: `Bearer ${token}` } }
);
// ~2kb for just the endpoint we need
```

Bundle impact: -34kb. CI bundle budget updated to 45kb max.
